title: Moe's Southwest Grill
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Nationwide franchise offering tacos, burritos, nachos, and rice bowls with choice of black or pinto beans, and organic tofu or veggies instead of meat. Dairy is used, so vegans need to specify. Food is made in front of you as you walk along a line. Fresh salsa bar. Chips and salsa comes with your order.
